  <brief_title>Comparison of Eprosartan/HCT Versus Enalapril/HCT in Hypertensives With Type II Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized Study Comparing the Efficacy of Combination Therapy of Eprosartan Respectively Ramipril With Low-Dose Hydrochlorothiazide and Moxonidine on Blood Pressure Levels in Patients With Hypertension and Associated Diabetes Mellitus Type 2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
